attributes.review: i downloaded the app because i was interested in what trump had been planning for the 2020 election, but when it FINALLY downloaded after 5 days of waiting it wouldn’t let me open the app still so i powered off my phone and i opened the app again than it worked. the app was EXTREMELY glitchy and when i clicked on one thing it showed me something else. i do not support this app whatsoever and i think it’s not safe for anyone to use. they ask for your phone number which is ok but they also ask for your zip code. and the fact that the app barely works just makes it a bit concerning. so i forgot about the app for a few days but i decided to get back on. what i saw was terrifying. it looked like i was on the dark web. a bunch of names and number kept popping up and i didn’t know what to do. after that i deleted the app. but things started moving in my room. and it’s things my family wouldn’t move. my desk ended up on the other side of my room my tv was on the floor i went to sleep with my closet door shut and when i woke up it was wide open. DELTE THIS APP before it’s too late.
